svg.title: Neuron-level diagram of the TensorFlow Keras network
svg.desc: Shows individual neurons for input, hidden, dropout, hidden, and output layers. Representative connections are drawn.
svg.text: Each dot is one neuron. Representative (not all) connections are shown for readability.
Model code: Input(784) → Dense(128, ReLU) → Dropout(0.2) → Dense(64, ReLU) → Dense(10, Softmax).
